- Install Nodejs 10.x
$ curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_10.x | sudo -E bash -
$ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

- Initialization NPM
$ npm init
  ...
  entry point: server.js
  test command: jest --forceExit --runInBand --coverage
  ...

- Install NPM Package
$ npm install

- Test Sources
$ npm run test

- Run Apps
$ node server.app
